def f_gold(tokens: List[str]) -> int:   # --- py stmt 1
    nums = []   # --- py stmt 2
    for t in tokens:   # --- py stmt 3
        if len(t) > 1 or t.isdigit():   # --- py stmt 4
            nums.append(int(t))   # --- py stmt 5
        else:   # --- py stmt 6
            if t == "+":   # --- py stmt 7
                nums[-2] += nums[-1]   # --- py stmt 8
            elif t == "-":   # --- py stmt 9
                nums[-2] -= nums[-1]   # --- py stmt 10
            elif t == "*":   # --- py stmt 11
                nums[-2] *= nums[-1]   # --- py stmt 12
            else:   # --- py stmt 13
                nums[-2] = int(nums[-2] / nums[-1])   # --- py stmt 14
            nums.pop()   # --- py stmt 15
    return nums[0]   # --- py stmt 16
